# Drop this file at the root of any repo as `.pii-allowlist`.
# One Python regex per line; keep entries narrow and explicit.
# Lines starting with `#` and blank lines are ignored.

# Common public/test addresses that OPF will flag as private_email.
(?i)^[^@\s]+@example\.(?:com|org|net)$
(?i)^[^@\s]+@test\.(?:com|org|net)$
(?i)^git@github\.com$
(?i)^[^@\s]+@users\.noreply\.github\.com$
